import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { FormBuilder, FormControl, FormGroup, Validators, } from '@angular/forms'; import ValidateForm from 'src/app/helpers/validateform'; @Component({ selector: 'app-signup', templateUrl: './signup.component.html', styleUrls: ['./signup.component.css'], }) export class SignupComponent implements OnInit { type: string = 'password'; isText: boolean = false; eyeIcon: string = 'fa-eye-slash'; signUpForm!: FormGroup; constructor(private fb: FormBuilder) {} ngOnInit(): void { this.signUpForm = this.fb.group({ firstName: ['', Validators.required], lastName: ['', Validators.required], userName: ['', Validators.required], email: ['', Validators.required], password: ['', Validators.required], }); } hideShowPass() { this.isText = !this.isText; this.isText ? (this.eyeIcon = 'fa-eye') : (this.eyeIcon = 'fa-eye-slash'); this.isText ? (this.type = 'text') : (this.type = 'password'); } onSubmit() { if (this.signUpForm.valid) { //---------------------------------// } else { ValidateForm.validateAllFormFields(this.signUpForm); } } }
